name: Kibuka (War God)
shortLoreBlurb: Kibuka (War God) is a deity from Buganda (Uganda) associated with war, sky. Linked to tempests and the rule of kings.
overlapsLinks: Athena (Greek), Indra (Vedic), Karttikeya (Hindu), Morrigan (Celtic), Perun (Slavic), Sekhmet (Egyptian), Thor (Norse), Zeus (Greek)
